</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[95,1103,2981,3010]" pageId="144" pageNumber="745" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="144.[95,1300,2543,3167]" box="[95,1103,2981,3010]" pageId="144" pageNumber="745">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[95,330,2981,3010]" pageId="144" pageNumber="745">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
The Angolan Vlei Rat is terrestrial and mainly diurnal.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
